label.value: lateral pectal fossa of the coxa

value.value: The fossa that is located laterally on the proximal margin of the coxa and accommodates the lateral coxal condyle of the pectus.

label.value: lateral coxal condyle of the pleuron

value.value: The condyle that is located distally on the lateral coxal articular process of the pleuron and inserts into the lateral pectal fossa of the coxa.
The fossa that is located on the coxa and accommodates the coxal condyle of the pleuron.

label.value: medial pectal fossa of the coxa

value.value: The pectal fossa of the coxa that accommodates the median coxal condyle of the pleuron.
The condyle that is located on the pectus and inserts into the pectal fossa of the coxa.

label.value: medial coxal condyle of the pectus

value.value: The coxal condyle of the pectus that inserts into the medial pectal fossa of the coxa.
